BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:qywjYjtgek87BPeaB-f3B
SUMMARY:Crowdsource Choir
DTSTAMP:20260411T111858Z
DTSTART:20260501T190000Z
DESCRIPTION:We’re continuing our Sing Seattle Songs theme—and once again\\\
	, you help shape the show by choosing the music. The songs may be born in 
	Seattle\\\, inspired by Seattle\\\, or made iconic through Seattle films a
	nd stories—but the final setlist will emerge from your votes. \\nChoose th
	e songs you want to sing by voting here. \\nYour selections will directly 
	influence what we learn\\\, layer\\\, and sing together in the room. \\nTo
	wn Hall is the perfect home for this gathering—a civic space where the peo
	ple of Seattle come together to express who we are\\\, where we come from\
	\\, and how our stories keep evolving. This night becomes a shared act of 
	remembrance and re-creation\\\, sung by the city itself. \\nNo rehearsals.
	 No sheet music. No choir robes. Just a room full of voices\\\, Seattle pr
	ide\\\, and the soundtrack of the city we love—raised together in harmony.
	 \\nYou help choose the songs. We become the choir.\n\nhttps://townhallsea
	ttle.org/event/crowdsource-choir-10/\n\nFrom Town Hall Seattle
URL:https://townhallseattle.org/event/crowdsource-choir-10/
LOCATION:The Wyncote NW Forum\\\, 1119 8th Ave (Entrance off Seneca St.)\\\
	, Seattle\\\, 98101\\\, United States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:town-hall-seattle
CATEGORIES:Town Hall Seattle
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT
END:VEVENT
